stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR
    [*] --> pending_review: AM 发起入职
    pending_review --> documents_incomplete: AM 审核/退回补资料
    documents_incomplete --> pending_review: 员工重新提交
    pending_review --> onboarding: AM 审核通过
    documents_incomplete --> onboarding: 资料补齐
    onboarding --> contract_signed: 合同签署完成
    contract_signed --> active: Job 1 自动激活\n(到达 Start Date)
    active --> on_leave: Job 4 自动切换\n(假期开始)
    on_leave --> active: Job 4 自动切换\n(假期结束)
    active --> offboarding: Ops 发起离职
    on_leave --> offboarding: Ops 发起离职
    offboarding --> terminated: 离职清算完成

    classDef auto fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#4CAF50,stroke-width:2px
    classDef manual fill:#E3F2FD,stroke:#2196F3,stroke-width:2px
    classDef terminal fill:#FFEBEE,stroke:#F44336,stroke-width:2px

    class active,on_leave auto
    class pending_review,documents_incomplete,onboarding,contract_signed,offboarding manual
    class terminated terminal
